sent [LCP ConfAck id=0xb <mru 1280> <asyncmap 0x0> <accomp>]
rcvd [LCP ConfRej id=0x1 <magic 0x7aa74ae7> <pcomp>]
sent [LCP ConfReq id=0x2 <asyncmap 0x0> <accomp>]
rcvd [LCP ConfAck id=0x2 <asyncmap 0x0> <accomp>]
